cwsd (1.3.3) noble; urgency=medium

  * rigctld: add optional rig.serial_speed config. Some hamlib backends default
    to a serial rate the local termios layer can't set (the QRPLabs QMX, model
    2057, defaults to 256000), so rig_open() failed silently and rigctld
    answered nothing to clients. Pin a standard rate to fix it.

 -- Adrian Scripca <benishor@gmail.com>  Wed, 08 Jul 2026 06:52:38 +0300

cwsd (1.3.2) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging; publish to the hamtools PPA.
  * Runs as a dedicated, unprivileged DynamicUser systemd service reading
    /etc/cwsd/cwsdrc (added to the dialout and audio groups).

